        "type": "element",
        "tag": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Accustomed to the rough-and-tumble fighting using whatever weapons happen to be at hand, you gain the following benefits:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Increase your Strength or Consititution score by 1, to a maximum of 20."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "You are proficient with improvised weapons."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Your unarmed strike uses a d4 for damage."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "When you hit a creature with an unarmed strike or an improvised weapon on your turn, you can use a bonus action to attempt to grapple the target."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "html": "<div id=\"page-content\">\n<p>Source: Player's Handbook</p>\n<p>Accustomed to the rough-and-tumble fighting using whatever weapons happen to be at hand, you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Increase your Strength or Consititution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>You are proficient with improvised weapons.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Your unarmed strike uses a d4 for damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>When you hit a creature with an unarmed strike or an improvised weapon on your turn, you can use a bonus action to attempt to grapple the target.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>"
